From 7efe316d368e00784a0e541c0e8b787f0d19562f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: LegionGames Dev <git@legiongames.ru>
Date: Fri, 10 Apr 2026 13:10:59 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 08/11] Fix AmneziaWG integration for v0.68.1

- Resolved merge conflicts with upstream v0.68.1
- Updated all wireguard/tun imports to amneziawg-go/tun
- Fixed proto.AmneziaConfig (regenerated from .proto)
- Fixed ice_bind.go API (ReceiverCreator interface)
- Added EngineServices struct
- Added AmneziaWG deps to go.mod + replace directives
- Built client (54MB) and management (73MB) binaries

Co-authored-by: Qwen-Coder <qwen-coder@alibabacloud.com>
